title: UFYB 9: Thought Work is a Feminist Act
itunes:title: Thought Work Is a Feminist Act
description:
In this short but important episode, I explain the immense benefits of investing in your mental and emotional health, why it's a feminist issue, and why you can’t afford not to begin this work in 2018.

Get full show notes and more information here: http://bit.ly/2D4q2Lj
